1. *Doručak* se sprema u 8 ujutru. (Breakfast is prepared at 8 in the morning.)
2. Moja porodica obično sprema *doručak* u kući. (My family usually prepares breakfast at home.)
3. Jutros nisam imao vremena za *doručak*. (I didn't have time for breakfast this morning.)
4. *Doručak* je najvažniji obrok u danu. (Breakfast is the most important meal of the day.)
5. *Doručkova* vremena je tokom vikenda odličan trenutak za porodične razgovore. (Breakfast time on weekends is a great moment for family conversations.)